      "parameters": {
        "width": 480,
        "height": 896,
        "content": "YouTube AI Automation Spy\n### How it works\n\n1. Triggers a scheduled workflow execution.\n2. Collects data from multiple YouTube channels based on set parameters.\n3. Merges and processes the received data with existing records.\n4. Applies custom logic to filter and refine the data.\n5. Appends the processed data into a Google Sheet.\n6. Ensures no duplicate data is appended through a deduplication step.\n\n### Setup steps\n\n- [ ] Configure Google Sheets API credentials for data retrieval and append operations.\n- [ ] Set up YouTube API credentials to access channel information.\n- [ ] Define the schedule for the trigger to automate the workflow execution.\n\n### Customization\n\nModify the JavaScript code nodes to alter data processing logic as needed."
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
